text: Annie Villiger (born 4 April 1914) was a Swiss diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1914 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss female divers Category:Olympic divers of Switzerland Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
